reviewText: Jack Canfield is a master story teller and he has some great ones on this DVD. I own lots of personal motivation materials, and this is one that I go back to often. It is motivational, touching and entertaining. If you are looking to reconnect with your purpose and find the motivation to work on your goals every day, look no further.
I really enjoyed the DVD.  He give a number of pointers regarding self-esteem.  It also comes with a MP3 version you can listen to on your player.
